# (small but real user-facing tool), 4 subcommands
# (launch/push/pull/watch) in single 966-line
# sprite-tool.fs, exercises EVERY MAJOR Gforth
# CLI PATTERN (`#! /usr/bin/env gforth` shebang,
# `\` line comments and `( ... )` inline,
# `create NAME N allot` static buffer allocation,
# `variable` globals, `{ var }` Gforth locals,
# `next-arg` stdlib primitive argv accessor,
# `s"..."  str=` literal-string-on-stack matching,
# nested `then`-chains for flag dispatch, hand-
